{
  "texts": [
    "GenAI alleviates some of the previous challenges of knowledge storage while creating new ones.",
    "GenAI introduces new sources of potential knowledge (e.g., knowledge captured in encyclopedias, dictionaries, books, scientific papers, literature, the press, etc.)",
    "that can be obtained without nudging.",
    "And GenAI itself produces new knowledge or, in some cases, existing knowledge that is newly synthesized-e.g., the summary and integration of reports and documents, responses to queries, and the capture of meeting notes, to name a few.",
    "The knowledge is then stored and made accessible for future reference."
  ]
}